description: Maui Wowi Hawaiian Coffees and Smoothies is as close as you can get to going to Hawaii without hopping on a plane (plus you’ll save tons of cash). You’ll find delicious Hawaiian coffees, all-natural fruit smoothies and lots of island attitude. Maui Wowi DC is a mini vacation from all things mundane – and all things corporate. There is nothing like Maui Wowi DC. No wonder people call us a “vacation in a cup!”
name: Maui Wowi
